definition.text: This command provides a mechanism to navigate to a Docs page or an specific anchor within a page.

paragraphs.text: docs.goto Project->Docs Page Category->Docs Page Name->Docs Page Anchor
Project : Is the project where the Node, Concept or Topic is defined.
Docs Page Category : Node, Concept or Topic.
Docs Page Name : For Nodes it is the type of node, for Concepts, the concept name, for topics, the topic's page name.
Docs Page Anchor : This parameter is optional. If present, it refers to an Docs Anchor paragraph defined within the page.
